modName: Temptress race CBBE texture and mesh fix
summary:
This mod fixes the texture and meshes on the Temptress race.

Allowing you to not have to use UMP.
descriptionHtml:
[b]This mod contains resources mad by other authors and no mesh or texture was created by me, I simply fixed some files and mad this mod for ease of access and mad it for people who don't know how to change things around in the DATA folder.




[/b]Here are all of the Mods visible;
Temptress Race http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/18717/?
CBBE http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
CBBE armor replacer http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3654/?

Before installing make sure you have the neck seam fix for Temptress to CBBE as well.

[b]Installation:
[/b]To install, all you need to do is place the Textures and Meshes files in there respective place in the DATA folder in the Skyrim directory.
author: Bandit4557
